# NEVPNConnectionError.pluginFailed

**Case**

An error code that indicates the VPN plugin failed unexpectedly.

## Declaration

```swift
case pluginFailed
```

## Plugin error codes

- **NEVPNConnectionError.pluginDisabled**: An error code that indicates the VPN plugin isn’t available or needs an update.
